body:
@yTakatsukasa thanks for adding the bit ops in #2751. Can you please look at the internal code coverage for this?  (https://codecov.io/gh/verilator/verilator/src/master/src/V3Const.cpp - you might need to login to see it).

There's a bunch of minor stuff I'm fine ignoring if you are, but currently all tests exit matchOrAndNot here https://github.com/verilator/verilator/blob/master/src/V3Const.cpp#L651 and we are never running the rest of the function. So might be worth adding a test to cover those cases.

Thanks.
